# Expression output-sensitivity fixture (GH #198).
#
# Linear mass-action chain  A --k1--> B --k2--> C  (all elementary, so the
# codegen sensitivity RHS engages and the IC axis is available), plus global
# functions exercising every addressable chain-rule dependency kind:
#   scaled() = scale*A_obs              parameter + observable
#   ratio()  = A_obs/(BC2+eps)          two observables + parameter
#   combo()  = scaled() + ratio()       earlier functions
#   tdep()   = k1*A_obs*time()          time (drops) + parameter + observable
# Observables (from obs_sens_chain.net): A_obs=A, BC2=B+2C, Total=A+B+C.
begin parameters
    1 k1    0.30
    2 k2    0.15
    3 scale 2.0
    4 eps   0.50
end parameters
begin species
    1 A() 100
    2 B() 0
    3 C() 0
end species
begin reactions
    1 1 2 k1 #A_to_B
    2 2 3 k2 #B_to_C
end reactions
begin groups
    1 A_obs 1
    2 BC2   2,2*3
    3 Total 1,2,3
end groups
begin functions
    1 scaled() scale*A_obs
    2 ratio() A_obs/(BC2+eps)
    3 combo() scaled()+ratio()
    4 tdep() k1*A_obs*time()
end functions
